{
 "name": "RPlog_Of_Diplomacy_and_Reprisal",
 "title": "Of Diplomacy and Reprisal",
 "summary": "Aboard the New Republic Star Destroyer Reprisal, flagship of the 2nd Fleet, Captain Stone leads a welcoming party in the starfighter hangar for the visiting Caspian ambassador Ambrosia Delgard, who arrives weary with her drooling toddler daughter Gabi on her hip. The junior officers Mitali and the diminutive Twi'lek Marine Wrista play host, charmed by the baby, while the pilots Aaden and Kegren'Te look on and the new transfer Midshipman Harrison Bach hangs back, unsure whether to approach. As Delgard trades pleasantries and her irreverent droid C4 embarrasses her, the docking of Commander Adam Shadow's contingent prompts a brief, formal meet-and-greet ahead of a joint investigation. The scene captures the bustle of shipboard protocol, the human touches of a tired diplomat and her child, and the careful courtesies of a fledgling Republic-Caspian collaboration.",
